results.name: BAPE x Superstar 'Mixed Camo'
results.story: Designed in collaboration with the legendary streetwear brand, the BAPE x adidas Superstar ‘Mixed Camo’ celebrates the classic silhouette’s half-century mark. The low-top features mismatched camo-print paneling in purple, red and blue, the contrasting hues offset by a solid black finish on the heel tab and rubber shell toe. The jumbled color blocking is accompanied by asymmetrical branding elements, including adidas’ signature three-stripes on the left side of each shoe and BAPE’s shooting star logo on the right. At the foot of each lace bed, BAPE dubraes shine in metallic gold.

results.name: adidas Yeezy Boost 350 V2 Ash Stone
results.story: The adidas Yeezy Boost 350 V2 ‘Ash Stone’ highlights subdued earth tones throughout its re-engineered Primeknit upper. The complementary blend of tan, brown and grey fibers is arranged in different weaves that create an intricate, patchwork-like design, offset by a coral-colored side stripe on the sneaker’s lateral side. The sock-like build is mounted on a full-length Boost midsole wrapped in semi-translucent rubber for added durability and support. This colorway launched exclusively in Europe, Russia, Ukraine and the Asia-Pacific region.

results.name: adidas Yeezy Boost 350 V2 Ash Blue
results.story: The adidas Yeezy Boost 350 V2 ‘Ash Blue’ carries a re-engineered Primeknit upper constructed from a blend of slate blue, grey and black fibers. A pale yellow hue distinguishes the post-dyed monofilament side stripe woven into the sneaker’s lateral side panel, delivering added breathability and an unexpected pop of color. The sock-like upper rides on a full-length Boost midsole, wrapped up in a semi-translucent rubber cage for improved stability and durability.

results.name: Wmns Terrex Skychaser XT Mid GTX 'Core Black'
results.story: The adidas women’s Terrex Skychaser XT Mid GTX ‘Core Black’ packs a responsive ride, thanks to the combination of a molded sockliner and full-length Boost midsole, partially encaged with a Promoderator plate for increased stability. Underfoot, a lugged Continental rubber outsole provides sure footing on uneven terrain. The mid-top carries a breathable black mesh upper, secured with a drawcord lacing system and reinforced with a waterproof Gore-Tex membrane. An EVA stabilization frame provides lightweight durability and support.

results.name: BAPE x Superstar 'White Black'
results.story: Created in partnership with the pioneering streetwear label, the BAPE x adidas Superstar ‘White Black’ celebrates 50 years of the sneaker icon. Asymmetrical branding is showcased on the white leather upper, with the left side of each shoe featuring adidas’ signature three-stripes, while the right side displays BAPE’s shooting star logo. Similarly, mismatched BAPE and adidas branding lands on each shoe’s tongue, heel tab and sockliner. BAPE lace locks in metallic gold represent the finishing touch.

results.name: Terrex Agravic BOA 'Black White'
results.story: The adidas Terrex Agravic BOA ‘Black White’ combines responsive cushioning with a rugged, trail-ready build. The sneaker’s black textile upper features stretchy bootie-style construction and a webbing pull tab at the heel for easy on and off. Tonal synthetic overlays provide added durability and support, while a BOA lacing system offers micro-adjustments on the go. The slip-on is mounted atop a full-length Boost midsole, supported by a lugged Continental rubber outsole.

results.name: Kid Cudi x Vadawam 326 'Dark Brown'
results.story: The Kid Cudi x adidas Vadawam 326 ‘Dark Brown’ highlights a blend of earth tones and vibrant accents on a retro-inspired silhouette named after the American rapper’s daughter, Vada. ‘326’ nods to her birthday and is printed on the shoe’s lateral collar. An integrated lacing system is supplemented by a trio of brown leather hook-and-loop straps, matching the midfoot overlays. Both the sneaker’s tongue and tooling are borrowed from the Artillery High, the latter equipped with adidas’ iconic Torsion bar.

results.name: UltraBoost 5.0 DNA J 'Oreo'
results.story: Developed for big kids, the adidas UltraBoost 5.0 DNA J ‘Oreo’ applies a simplistic black and white color scheme to the Primeknit upper, featuring sock-like construction that wraps the foot in lightweight support. Black textile is utilized on the heel counter and midfoot cage, integrated into the lacing system for a feeling of lockdown. The sneaker is mounted on a full-length Boost midsole, underpinned by a Stretchweb outsole made with grippy Continental rubber.

results.name: adidas Terrex Free Hiker Human Race Triple Black Pack
results.story: The Pharrell x adidas Terrex Free Hiker Zip ‘Triple Black’ is taken from a monochromatic footwear collection designed in partnership with the multifaceted creative. The sneaker-boot hybrid features a knit upper lined in a water-proof Gore-Tex membrane. Tonal Human Race branding adorns a zippered sheath that covers the laces and gives the high-cut silhouette a sleek look. Responsive cushioning arrives via a full-length Boost midsole, painted black and reinforced by a high-traction rubber outsole.

results.name: Trae Young x Top Ten High 'Ice Trae'
results.story: The Trae Young x adidas Top Ten High ‘Ice Trae’ delivers a pristine colorway of the vintage ‘70s hoops shoe specially made for the star NBA athlete. A clean white finish is executed on the glossy patent leather upper, accented with a collar overlay in a gradient blend of orange and red. Trae Young’s jersey number adorns the sneaker’s leather tongue tag. The high-top is mounted on a pale blue midsole, supported by a translucent outsole that reveals an oversized Ice Trae graphic.

results.name: adidas NMD Hu Pharrell Human Race Triple Black Pack
results.story: The Pharrel x adidas NMD Human Race ‘Triple Black’ is taken from a monochromatic pack designed in partnership with the multi-hyphenate creative. Launching alongside matching blacked-out editions of the adidas 0 To 60, Terrex Trailmaker Mid, and Terrex Free Hiker Zip, this pair features a breathable Primeknit upper mounted on a full-length Boost midsole. ‘Breathe’ is inscribed in tonal block lettering on the vamp of the right shoe, while ‘Thoughts’ is stamped on the left.

results.name: UltraBoost 5.0 DNA J 'Grey'
results.story: The adidas UltraBoost 5.0 DNA J ‘Grey’ offers a neutral colorway of a responsive running shoe built for big kids. The greyscale Primeknit upper is engineered to hug the foot for a sock-like fit. Tonal canvas construction is utilized on the heel counter and midfoot cage, integrated into the lacing system for an increasingly locked-in fit as the laces are cinched. The sneaker rides on a full-length Boost midsole, supported by a Stretchweb Continental rubber outsole.

results.name: adidas 0 To 60 STMT Human Race Triple Black Pack
results.story: The Pharrell x adidas BYW 0 To 60 ‘Triple Black’ is drawn from a monotone footwear collection made in partnership with the prolific creative. This refreshed take on the vintage hoops shoe features a zippered shroud for a streamlined aesthetic. Tonal Human Race branding is inscribed on an adjustable hook-and-loop strap wrapped around the ankle. Responsive cushioning comes courtesy of a podular Boost midsole, modeled after adidas’ Feet You Wear technology from the mid ‘90s.

results.name: adidas Terrex Trailmaker Mid Human Race Triple Black Pack
results.story: Launching as part of a monochromatic footwear collection with the multi-hyphenate creative, the Pharrell x adidas Terrex Trailmaker Mid GTX ‘Triple Black’ delivers a stealthy take on a versatile hiking shoe built for comfort. Ghillie lacing secures a breathable textile knit upper fortified with an EVA stability frame and lined in waterproof Gore-Tex. The outdoor silhouette rides on a lightweight EVA midsole, supported underfoot by an off-road Traxion outsole.

Five Ten Freerider Pro 'Grey Halo Blue'
results.story: The adidas Five Ten Freerider Pro ‘Grey Halo Blue’ updates the mountain biking shoe with a color-blocked upper made with quick-drying synthetic materials. For added breathability, perforated detailing is added to the urethane-reinforced toe box. The low-profile silhouette is mounted on a molded EVA midsole, which acts in tandem with an Ortholite sockliner for cushioned comfort. Underfoot, the Stealth S1 rubber outsole features a Dotty rubber tread for optimal grip on and off the pedal.

results.name: Five Ten Freerider 'Grey Black'
results.story: The adidas Five Ten Freerider ‘Grey Black’ applies neutral tones to a versatile flat-pedal mountain biking shoe. Ventilated black mesh on the upper is reinforced with grey suede overlays and a matching synthetic leather heel wrap. In lieu of adidas’ traditional three-stripe branding, a Five Ten logo decorates the lateral quarter panel. The low-top sneaker is mounted on a molded one-piece cupsole, built with high-friction Stealth S1 rubber and a pedal-ready Dotty tread underfoot.

results.name: Wmns Five Ten Freerider Pro 'Hazy Emerald'
results.story: The adidas women’s Five Ten Freerider Pro ‘Hazy Emerald’ highlights a monochromatic color scheme on a flat-pedal mountain biking shoe built for all-day comfort. The quick-drying synthetic upper is enhanced with a perforated toe box for added breathability and textured urethane overlays at the toe and heel for abrasion-resistant durability. Lightweight cushioning is provided by a molded EVA midsole, supported underfoot by a Stealth S1 rubber outsole with a Dotty rubber tread for superior pedal control.

results.name: Five Ten Freerider Pro 'Core Black'
results.story: The adidas Five Ten Freerider Pro ‘Core Black’ delivers a stealthy colorway of the performance mountain biking shoe. An ebony finish saturates the quick-drying synthetic upper, save for Five Ten and Freerider Pro branding on the sneaker’s lateral side. Enhanced breathability comes courtesy of perforated detailing on the urethane-reinforced toe box. The low-top rides on a lightweight EVA midsole, its sidewalls partially wrapped by a Dotty-tread Stealth S1 rubber outsole.

results.name: Fucking Awesome x Experiment 1 'Collegiate Royal'
results.story: The Fucking Awesome x adidas Experiment 1 ‘Collegiate Royal’ blends heritage style with the street-honed sensibilities of Jason Dill’s skate brand. The soccer-inspired low-top makes use of a royal blue textile upper with contrasting off-white leather overlays throughout. Navy leather three-stripes are integrated into the lacing system, while the woven tongue tag shows off an archival graphic with dual adidas and Fucking Awesome branding. A gum rubber outsole provides slip-resistant traction underfoot.

results.name: Donovan Mitchell x Top Ten High RB 'D.O.N.'
Wmns Five Ten Freerider 'Wild Teal'
results.story: The adidas women’s Five Ten Freerider ‘Wild Teal’ delivers a mountain biking shoe that blends performance-driven details with casual style. The upper is constructed from breathable green mesh with tonal suede overlays and a grey synthetic leather heel wrap. Both numerals are integrated into the Five Ten logo that adorns the lateral quarter panel, while a woven Freerider tag is affixed to the collar. Underfoot, the outsole features Stealth S1 rubber construction with a Dotty tread.

results.name: Fucking Awesome x Experiment 2 'Crystal White'
results.story: Created in partnership with Jason Dill’s skate brand, the Fucking Awesome x adidas Experiment 2 ‘Crystal White’ delivers a monochromatic leather low-top inspired by classic basketball shoes from the ‘80s and ‘90s. Exterior branding is limited to a gold Trefoil stamped on the heel tab and a woven FA tongue tag. A contrasting royal blue finish is applied to the sockliner, embellished with a debossed Fucking Awesome print. A semi-translucent rubber cupsole anchors the layered build.

results.name: adidas Forum Mid Ivy Park Icy Park Cream White (W)
results.story: The Ivy Park x adidas Forum Mid ‘Cream White’ is taken from the ‘Icy Park’ collection, developed in partnership with Beyonce’s streetwear brand and featuring a wintry Alpine theme. The vintage hoops shoe is updated with a premium leather and suede build in neutral white and cream tones. An adjustable strap wraps around the collar, featuring a padded interior lined in soft terry cloth for a comfortable fit. The mid-top is mounted on a rubber midsole, enhanced with an EVA wedge and supported by a gum rubber outsole.

results.name: Ivy Park x Wmns Super Sleek Boot 'Icy Park'
results.story: Launching as part of an Alpine-themed collection with Beyonce’s athleisure brand, the Ivy Park x adidas women’s Super Sleek Boot ‘Icy Park’ features a high-cut collar on a premium leather and suede upper. Metal hardware and an elastic bungee cord wrapped around the heel add to the sneaker-boot’s mountaineering aesthetic. The towering silhouette is mounted on an exaggerated gum rubber sole unit, featuring a herringbone traction pattern for reliable grip.

results.name: adidas Ultra Boost Ivy Park Icy Park (W)
results.story: The Ivy Park x adidas UltraBoost 4.0 ‘Ivy Park’ gives the responsive running shoe an alabaster makeover, courtesy of Beyonce’s athleisure brand. White Primeknit makes up the breathable composition of the upper, secured with drawcord lacing and an off-white midfoot cage. The same neutral hue is applied to the molded heel counter, featuring embossed Ivy Park branding on the lateral side. The lightweight build is mounted on a Boost midsole, supported by a Continental gum rubber outsole.

results.name: adidas Sleek Boot Ivy Park Icy Park (W)
Ivy Park x Wmns Sleek Boot 'Icy Park'
results.story: Launching as part of a larger collection with Beyonce’s athleisure brand, the Ivy Park x adidas women’s Sleek Boot ‘Icy Park’ blends streetwear style with alpine-ready details. The retro-inspired sneaker-boot hybrid features a premium blend of white leather and tonal suede on the quarter panel, tongue and collar. Speed hooks and D-ring eyelets are integrated into the lacing system, while a bungee cord around the heel allows the shoe to be clipped onto a backpack or bag. The gum rubber platform sole features a herringbone traction pattern for superior grip.

results.name: adidas Supersleek 72 Ivy Park Icy Park (W)
results.story: Launching as part of an Alpine-themed collection with Beyonce’s athleisure brand, the Ivy Park x adidas women’s Super Sleek 72 ‘Icy Park’ features an exaggerated double-stacked midsole in a pristine white finish. The sneaker’s platform tooling is countered by a low-profile upper, constructed from white leather with off-white suede overlays that include the Samba’s signature T-toe. An integrated lacing system includes bungee detailing wrapped around the heel, allowing the shoe to be clipped onto a carryall.

results.name: adidas Forum Mid Ivy Park Icy Park Silver (W)
results.story: The Ivy Park x adidas Forum Mid ‘Silver Metallic’ is drawn from the ‘Icy Park’ collection, an alpine-themed joint venture developed in partnership with Beyonce’s athleisure brand. This refreshed take on the vintage hoops shoe features a reflective metallic silver finish throughout leather upper, secured with an integrated lacing system and an adjustable ankle strap. The mid-top rests on a grey rubber midsole, enhanced with an EVA wedge and reinforced by a tacky gum rubber outsole.

results.name: Wmns Five Ten Trailcross LT 'Legacy Green'
results.story: The adidas women’s Five Ten Trailcross LT ‘Legacy Green’ delivers a versatile low-top that can be used for mountain biking or hiking. A military khaki hue is executed on the mesh and synthetic upper, accented with Five Ten branding in Signal Coral. An open mesh tongue provides added breathability, while binding around the low-cut collar offers abrasion-free comfort. The sneaker sits atop a lightweight EVA midsole, supported underfoot by a Stealth Phantom Dotty rubber outsole.

results.name: Five Ten Freerider Pro 'Black Red'
results.story: Five Ten Freerider Pro 'Black Red' showcases a simplistic two-tone finish on a mountain biking shoe built with a quick-drying synthetic upper. A crimson Five Ten logo on the lateral quarter panel provides a contrasting pop of color, while perforated detailing on the urethane-reinforced toe box yields enhanced breathability. The low-top sits on a red-hued EVA midsole, underpinned by a Stealth S1 rubber outsole with a Dotty tread for superior traction on and off the pedal.
